Database
=============================
RDBMS : relational database management system
There are following products that will come under RDBMS:


-my sql server		**
-ms sql server
-oracle
-ibm db2
-congnose
-mongodb
-sqllite 

Server/host : localhost   or ipaddress
user    : root
password : root

dbname :	
		hrms
		sales
	

SQL Command
==================
show databases;			--list of existing database
create database sales;		--create new database
use sales;			--switch database
create table customer		--create new table 
	(
	cid int,
	cname varchar(100)
	)

	 
desc tblname;		--show table structure 
select * from customer;			-- show data , * : show all columns

select cname,cid from customer;  --show one column

select * from customer			--filter rows 
where cid =1;	

--save data 
insert into customer(cid,cname)
values(11,'raman');


--delete row
delete from customer;  --remove all rows

delete from customer where cid  =1;  --delete selected rows 


--update data 
update customer 
set cname ='jatin'
where cid =2;



	




	
		
